705577f-b.title: Brooklyn: Marcy Avenue - Monroe Street
705577f-b.text:
Marcy Avenue, north from Monroe Street, showing a
W. P. A. street improvement project. In the left fore-
gTound, at the S. W. corner of Gates Aenue, is St. Georges
Church. View 2 shows the avenue, north from Cuincy Street
and the "E1" on Lexington Avenue.
June 27, 1935
Views 1,2
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
